{"tid":617534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成人展開鑼　女優行騷即場賣制服","createTime":"2018-04-05T04:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T04:29:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":26,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"02c0bc70526c928e2695c419c03ba4cd55b7fb50","tid":617534,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:56:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180405/20352425\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180405%2F20352425&d=OBFoKsiX%2BH3Sc29xeXp75tibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=86f599c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180405%2F20352425&h=f536fac4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180405/20352425</a><br />\n<br />\n成人展開鑼　女優行騷即場賣制服<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】全港首個對公眾開放的成人嘉年華「18+ Central」，今日起一連四日於中環海濱活動空間舉行。今年大會邀請友田彩也香、若月瑪麗亞等5位日本知名女優來港與支持者見面，她們將參與其中兩場服裝騷，穿過的制服及裝飾會即場拍賣。友田及若月期待與粉絲會面，又指希望日後有機會與成龍合作演戲。<br />\n<br />\n友田及若月昨接受訪問時認為，本港社會規範、審查制度非常嚴格，令成人電影發展未如其他地區般蓬勃，但這不代表本港落後，舉例指是次成人商，主辦單位把性玩具和商品於大庭廣眾展示，算是進步。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180405/large/a0503a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180405%2Flarge%2Fa0503a.gif&h=dcb0b326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩名女優昨在銅鑼灣品嚐港式小食，吸引港男與她們自拍。朱永倫攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讚港男體貼　想與成龍合作<br />\n<br />\n被問到對港男的印象，友田認為他們遠較日本的支持者害羞，即使部份人或比較熱情，但不敢表露出來。但她認為港男也有優勝之處，就是事事都照顧女性利益為先，體貼有風度。她又提到，支持女優不再是男士專利，近年不少女士都視女優為偶像，如自己曾遇過一名女粉絲，會把和她的合照設為手機的背景圖片。她認為女粉絲較傾向認為女優年輕貌美、可愛，因而產生憧憬。<br />\n<br />\n最近兩年才出席海外活動的若月則表示，要成為出色女優首要認真、專注及尊重工作，她又希望讓大眾明白女優不是只懂拍AV。至於日後會否如部份日本女優般參演本港電影，她們說希望有機會，最想與成龍合作，讓她們近距離看他打功夫。<br />\n<br />\n■記者于健民<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180405/large/a0503b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180405%2Flarge%2Fa0503b.gif&h=523fb4c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f62d00223955e26acfca5a2a2b9e701b84537e31","tid":617534,"uid":40470,"like":122,"dislike":4,"score":118,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T04:58:03.000Z","msg":"連登毒撚只會在家download AV打J"},{"pid":"14bb10988b2d3cf53414677ac2696915e20c74a8","tid":617534,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:01:21.000Z","msg":"有否痴漢就地正法"},{"pid":"9467c271086aae92e528be30deb253a743e727ea","tid":617534,"uid":13592,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:04:04.000Z","msg":"有冇打J區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9d62c28880fa91a20a1c9dd3d99ca6845163d1","tid":617534,"uid":164626,"like":123,"dislike":2,"score":121,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:04:37.000Z","msg":"想與成龍合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a510b7dc47f8f670de3c509de5e2fed9f7984d","tid":617534,"uid":80481,"like":143,"dislike":6,"score":137,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:04:47.000Z","msg":"Av女優還av女優，女優還女優，不可混為一談"},{"pid":"225203a3e67581df587b74f43c15f3d4cda89b9d","tid":617534,"uid":46947,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:05:36.000Z","msg":"記住打完J後去握手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520abb1a9b8271895028f435b5d3a2c33db9e91a","tid":617534,"uid":34013,"like":61,"dislike":4,"score":57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:10:48.000Z","msg":"$380門票 痴撚線"},{"pid":"fb8dbff95202c87130b689b17d54a3ac6fc22665","tid":617534,"uid":79959,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:18:46.000Z","msg":"入場費包口交?"},{"pid":"63ed23d5f43c58c2ec05db9a86880e7c170cbc33","tid":617534,"uid":155818,"like":2,"dislike":